    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review employment support including ESA available to autistic individuals",
        "additional_details": "I\u2019m calling on the Government to review the financial support that is available to autistic individuals, including Employment and Support Allowance (ESA), so that they can achieve paid employment.",
        "background": "In the UK only 32% of autistic individuals are in some kind of paid work. That statistic shockingly shows that the vast majority of autistic individuals are unemployed, with many more only in low-paid part-time work. ",
